App-RemoteGnokii version 0.000_001
==================================

RemoteGnokii is a set of scripts that add networking to gnokii-smsd.
With them, all messages received are forwarded to a given phone
number, and messages can be sent via the HTTP gateway provided by
RemoteGnokii.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

 * Config::Any
 * File::Slurp
 * File::Which
 * Plack::Request

